title: Red Raiders stay in the top 10 poll - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Red Raiders stay in the top 10 poll - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: NEW ORLEANS, La. – The Texas Tech track and field remained in the top 10 in the sixth installment of the U.S. Track & Field and Cross Country Coaches Association (USTFCCCA) poll released Monday afternoon.
